## The "Marie Kondo" Test for UI

Ask yourself about each element:

1. If I delete this, will anyone miss it? If not, delete it.
2. Is this thing just repeating what something else already says? (If yes, pick a favorite and move on.)
3. Would a user even notice if it vanished? If not, remove it.
